} Listing 11-11: Three tests with three different names 如果我们不传递任何参数运行测试，正如我们之前看到的，所有测试都会并行运行： $ cargo test Compiling adder v0.1.0 (file:///projects/adder) Finished `test` profile [unoptimized + debuginfo] target(s) in 0.62s Running unittests src/lib.rs (target/debug/deps/adder-92948b65e88960b4) running 3 tests
