2 | let x = (let y = 6); | ^^^ | = note: only supported directly in conditions of `if` and `while` expressions warning: unnecessary parentheses around assigned value --> src/main.rs:2:13 |
2 | let x = (let y = 6); | ^ ^ | = note: `#[warn(unused_parens)]` on by default
help: remove these parentheses |
2 - let x = (let y = 6);
